    "English": "Energy shield that protects spacecraft from laser fire, in-flight projectiles and accidental space debris interaction.<br><br>User is advised that <span class=\"name name-catalyst\">catalytic elements</span> are required to recharge device.<br><br>Operates automatically once constructed within user's starship inventory.",
